We shall start by exploring the basics of the language. This is a synopsis of things that I learned from Duolingo. 
Some commonly used names in this article would be Marcus and Corinna. 

Female: Femine
Male: Vivir
Girl: Puella
Boy: Puer
He: Is
She: Es
Is: Est
Are: Es
It: Cest
Domi: Home
Dormit: Sleeps
Scribit: Writes
